name: Day 15: Interactive Illustrations
description:
Welcome to the final day of the Figma prototype challenge! In this challenge we will be creating interactive illustrations. In the file you will find:

  1. A gif demonstrating the animation
  2. A workspace for you to build your prototype
  3. The built out prototype to use as reference
  4. Other interactive illustrations from the community


Feel free to recreate the one I made or make a new one all of your own. Whatever you choose to do, don't forget to post a Remix or publish a new Community File with the tag FigmaPrototypeChallenge! Happy prototyping! ðŸŽ‰
